					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Log in to the Horizon 7 Console. From the left pane, navigate to Settings &gt;&gt; Global Settings. In the right pane, click the "General Settings" tab. Find the “Connection Server Session Timeout” value.

If "Connection Server Session Timeout" is set to more than 15 minutes, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
