If the "Reauthenticate Secure Tunnel Connections After Network Interruption" setting is set to "No", this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Log in to the Horizon 7 Console. From the left pane, navigate to Settings &gt;&gt; Global Settings. In the right pane, click the "Security Settings" tab. Click "Edit". Check the box next to "Reauthenticate secure tunnel connections after network interruption". Click "OK".</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
