If the "Disconnect Applications and Discard SSO Credentials for Idle Users" setting is set to "Never", this is a finding.

If the "Disconnect Applications and Discard SSO Credentials for Idle Users" setting is set to greater than "120" minutes (two hours), this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
