					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Log in to the Horizon 7 Console. From the left pane, navigate to Settings &gt;&gt; Servers. In the right pane, select the "Connection Servers" tab. For each Connection Server listed, select the server and click "Edit". Click the "Authentication" tab. Under "Horizon Authentication", find the value in the drop-down below "Unauthenticated Access".

